longBusinessSummary: OncoSil Medical Limited, a medical device company, focuses on the development and commercialization of localized radiation therapy for the treatment of pancreatic and distal cholangiocarcinoma in worldwide. Its lead product is OncoSil, a brachytherapy device indicated for the treatment of patients with locally advanced pancreatic cancer in combination with gemcitabine-based chemotherapy. OncoSil Medical Limited was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Macquarie Park, Australia.
